data.description: Lovely 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom with an open floorplan located in Wylie ISD.  Enjoy sipping your morning coffee on your large, covered front porch! Large living area with a wood burning brick fireplace. The kitchen boasts gorgeous cabinetry, quartz counters, stainless steel appliances, & a great island! Dining area is off the kitchen making entertaining easy & a half bath off the kitchen. Large owners' bedroom with plenty of space for all your furniture, large ensuite with dual sinks, storage, & a fabulous, tiled walk-in shower with THREE shower heads & separate tub to relax in! Spacious guest bedrooms, large laundry room with storage & sink. Out back is a storage shed, RV carport attached to a 20x15 shop with electric and a massive backyard ready for your ideas!! Schedule a showing soon, this one won't last long! $10,000 Buyer Concession to spend how you'd like! Whether it be closing cost or rate buy down!
